               <msContents>
                  <summary><title type="supplied">Legends of Saints</title>. <note>Copies of Latin vitae. As the originals
                     are now lost, this manuscript is now the primary source of numerous vitae of
                     Danish saints, e.g. the vita of St. Theodgarus or Thøger of Jutland who founded
                     the first church in Vestervig in Thy, Northern Jutland, and was celebrated in
                     Thy as their local saint.</note></summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
               </msContents>
